data.description: This 1879 square foot single family home has 4 bedrooms and 3.0 bathrooms. This home is located at 8901 Valleybrook Rd, Birmingham, AL 35206.
data.whatILove:
This Lovely 4 Bedroom, 3 Bathroom House On a 17, 653 square foot Corner Lot In The Glenbrook Estates II Community Has A Full Finished Basement with a Separate Entrance that Features 1 Bedroom, a Laundry Room, An Entertainment/Media Room, An Ideal Home Office Space and a Full Bathroom which can easily be set up as a Separate Apartment with $750+ per month in income potential.

Upstairs the Home Features 3 Bedrooms (including a Master Suite with its own full bathroom and 1 large and 1 walk-in closet). The Kitchen has been updated and looks out on an open concept dining area next to a living room with a fireplace. There is also a Separate Formal Dining/Living Room that looks out of the Large Picture Window with serene views seen from the front of the House.

The Home also features 2 working fireplaces (Upstairs and Downstairs), A Large Back Yard with a Brick Patio Deck, A 2 Car Carport and A Kitchen Entrance.

The Roof, Central Heat & Air, Dishwasher and Water Heater Have All Been Updated.

This House Has Been The Perfect Home for Us to Raise Our 3 Children In and Now We Are Hoping It Will Bless Another Growing Family The Same Way.

P.S. We Will Only Entertain Serious Offers From True Cash Buyers. Anything Less Than $160K (Net Cash At Closing) Will Be Rejected... Period.

We Are Open to "Creative Financing" Options That Come With A Minimum $50K Cash Down Payment with Negotiated Terms.
